title: Truth doesn't exists
---
body:

 > I don't know such thing as truth.

Truth is what people believe to be the truth.

Truth can be for some people perception.

For practical reasons we can create truth as a percentage.

If something derives:
* from tangible verifiable facts it's true.
* from tangible facts it's true.
* from psychology it's a story.
